{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c1f9dc379f","title":"有关右派分子陆清福的判刑、摘帽和平反材料","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0ada4fc498","index":0,"year":1958,"month":7,"day":15,"articleId":"c1f9dc379f"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1b92b2b371","type":"title","text":"有关右派分子陆清福的判刑、摘帽和平反材料","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"6f0a652bde","type":"subtitle","text":"四川省宝兴县人民法院关于陆清福的刑事判决书","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"17b45d61e7","type":"subtitle","text":"法刑判[58]字第23号；1958.07.15","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"af5e035ae7","type":"paragraph","text":"陆清福，男，汉族，现年25岁，雅安县人。地主成份，学生出身，现住宝兴县城关镇。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"13ace12547","type":"paragraph","text":"陆清福思想一贯反动，趁我党整风之机大肆向党进攻，不仅赞同“党天下”、“清一色”等反动言论，还大肆宣扬鼓吹；组织陆、罗右派联盟，阴谋策划反党方案，情节严重恶劣，触犯刑律，特判决如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"3fd1e8e008","type":"paragraph","text":"管制四年。管制期中剥夺一切政权利。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"5b87361242","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九五八年七月十五日(法院大印)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"f0bf7016fe","type":"appellation","text":"附：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"996bc6bd42","type":"subtitle","text":"中共雅安县委员会关于摘掉陆清福右派帽子通知书","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"46dd7f89a9","type":"subtitle","text":"1978.05.26","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"81adec27a9","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央(78)11号文件关于全部摘掉右派分子帽子的通知，于1978年5月26日摘掉陆清福右派帽子。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"b7f046211e","type":"paragraph","text":"特此通知。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"6c2bf7b927","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共雅安县委员会1978年5月26日(由四川省雅安县革命委员会统战组代印)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"fb630c4626","type":"subtitle","text":"陆清福宝兴县人民法院刑事裁定书","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"8e54c1813a","type":"subtitle","text":"法裁[78]字第38号； 1979.04.20","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"b2ceadc13f","type":"paragraph","text":"陆清福，男，汉族，现年48岁。地主成份，学生出身。现住宝兴县城关镇，原县人民委员会委员、财政科长。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"db4bb0df1c","type":"paragraph","text":"陆清福因反党反社会主义一案，于一九五八年七月十五日，被我院判处管制四年。管制期中剥夺一切政治权利。经复查：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"df966f5ab1","type":"paragraph","text":"陆清福被划为极右分子问题，根据中发[78]55号文件精神，已改正。为此，定罪判刑不当，特裁定如下：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"0fed2bc875","type":"paragraph","text":"撤销原判，恢复政治名誉。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"},{"id":"eefcfba95b","type":"paragraph","text":" 宝兴县人民法院一九七九年四月二十日(法院大印)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f"}],"page":{"id":"d36aea6b0e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c1f9dc379f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}